t-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Yes, you heard that right.&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Forget the conventional “buying your significant other” flowers on Valentine’s Day and go ahead and buy them for yourself. It’ll brighten up your space and you can smell the roses (literally), while giving yourself an applause for giving YOU some extra love this Valentine’s day.&nbsp;</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606180375519" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606180375519"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: 700; font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 35px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;"><br></span></p><p><font face="Montserrat"><b>8. Disconnect to Connect&nbsp;</b></font></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606180489582" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606180489582"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">While we’re all for using an app to make a special dinner reservation or to read up on things to do this Valentine’s Day, there truly is no app to help you connect with the people right in front of you.</p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">It’s amazing how much space you can create for love, laughter, and good conversation when you disconnect from your screens.&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Whether you’re staying in by yourself, going over to a friends house, or heading out on a date, be present and ditch the phone for a few hours.&nbsp;</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606180390316" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606180390316"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: 700; font-family: Montserrat; font-size: 35px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;"><br></span></p><p><font face="Montserrat"><b>9. Sleep In</b></font></p></div></div><!--gfsplit--><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" id="e-1606180444512" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1606180444512"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Now we’re not saying don’t show up to your morning meeting, but we are condoning the healthy practice of treating yourself to an extra half hour, hour of sleep!&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Forget the guilt and remember all the benefits sleep has on your metabolism, cell rehabilitation leading to better skin, focus and retention of information, the list goes on and on. Stay in bed and repeat after us, “sleeping will do me (and my skin) good”.</p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;"><br></p><p class="" style="margin-bottom: 15px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 1.3px; text-align: start;">Lastly,  Happy Valentine’s Day❤️</p></div></div><!--gfsplit--></div><div id="divContentBk"></div><!--End_Gem_Page_Main_Editor-->
